description: Like no shaved ice you've ever had!  Yeti Sunshine's delicious snowballs are made of super-soft, finely shaved ice onto which we pour our unique, handmade flavors - crafted from real fruits and herbs.  Our fruit flavors are made with juice, pure cane sugar, filtered water and nothing else!  No food coloring or preservatives ever come near our syrups. Every step is carefully taken so that you receive an ideal snowball bursting with fresh sweet fruit flavor.
name: Yeti Sunshine
